Encryption.description:
Encryption class for encrypting text using the crypto module 

	var encryptor = new simpleportal.Encryption('sample');
	var isequeal = encryptor.authenticate('ENCRYPTED TEXT FROM DATABASE');

Logger.description:
Server console can be written to a filestream or directly to the console, with standard log formats

	//During Server start
	var logger = new simpleportal.Logger({root:'../log', access:'access.log', log:'simple_node.log',"console":"true"});

Server.description:
Simpleportal server, connectjs server wrapped with usefull functions from Simpleportal

	Example:

	var app = new simpleportal.Server();

	app.createServer();

